text: Nikolskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Miyakinsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 59 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 8 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Nikolskoye, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
